    note right of Unbound
        Created by no-arg constructor.
        bind() must be called before accept().
        setPerformancePreferences() only effective before bind().
        setReceiveBufferSize() should be called before bind() for large TCP windows.
    end note

    note right of Closed
        Terminal state. close() is idempotent.
        setOption(), getOption(), setReuseAddress() throw IOException if called on closed socket.
        accept() throws if called on closed socket.
    end note
